originalText.text: Morgan is such an amazing physical therapist. Morgan is incredibly easy to work with while being so knowledgeable. She gets to the core of the problem and makes sure you're comfortable performing all the exercises.  There's no other physical therapist I would recommend! She also does personal training which was a huge plus!

originalText.text: I have been working with Morgan on a regular basis for the past two years and have nothing but absolute praise for her and the incredible work she does.  Morgan is extremely intelligent and skilled in her field.  She is thoughtful and takes a customized and tailored approach with her patients in order to optimize health and healing.  She’s caring, asks the right questions and always listens.  I am very fortunate to have found Morgan and take comfort in the fact that I have her on my side as an incredibly talented healthcare professional and someone who always has my best interests in mind.

originalText.text: Morgan Rose Manasse, DPT brought me back from a shoulder injury recently and I will be forever grateful.  A slip on the ice didn’t seem that bad at first…but it turns out it was.  I swim as my physical and mental exercise and I was simply not able to do it after I hit that ice.  Morgan patiently got me back up swimming a mile a day, 4-5x a week and did so in ways I would never have known to do.  She is an amazing practitioner of her craft,  and considered the holistic ”me” in total when directing my recovery.  If you are looking for a partner to guide you in your physical health -  strength, endurance, flexibility, range of motion, bulking up, or bringing it back down - you would be fortunate indeed to have her as your guide.

originalText.text: Morgan is an exceptional physical therapist. She takes the time to understand your specific issues and tailors a program that is focused on addressing them. I had debilitating neck pain before seeing her which thanks to her is now under control.

originalText.text: Great experience with Morgan. She was professional, excellent with working my pain issue, and spent the full session not only educating me on how to better manage and treat the issue but also made me feel relaxed and comfortable the entire time. The facility is well designed and had all the equipment needed for my sessions. Thanks Morgan!
